node.text:
Everyone knows fishing, traveling, and sports are my passions! My parents have always been my role models and encouraged me to do what I love. I wouldn’t be able to do what I love every day if I was controlled by an addiction to cigarettes. I want to encourage everyone to stay tobacco-free. I want to live a long, healthy life that’s free from cigarettes! 
@therealcost #therealcost
